37212>>>>>    Function SetUserPassword String sLoginName String sPassword Returns Boolean
37214>>>>>        Handle hoUserDD
37214>>>>>        Integer iErr
37214>>>>>        Get phoUserDD to hoUserDD
37215>>>>>        
37215>>>>>        //  Find the user
37215>>>>>        Send Clear of hoUserDD
37216>>>>>        Move sLoginName to WebAppUser.LoginName
37217>>>>>        Send Find of hoUserDD EQ Index.1
37218>>>>>        If (not(Found)) Begin
37220>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37221>>>>>            Function_Return False
37222>>>>>        End
37222>>>>>>
37222>>>>>        
37222>>>>>        If (not(CreatePasswordHash(Self, Trim(sPassword), &sPassword))) Begin
37224>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37225>>>>>            Function_Return False
37226>>>>>        End
37226>>>>>>
37226>>>>>        Set Field_Changed_Value of hoUserDD Field WebAppUser.Password to sPassword
37227>>>>>        Get Request_Validate of hoUserDD to iErr
37228>>>>>        If (iErr) Begin
37230>>>>>            Send Clear of hoUserDD
37231>>>>>            Function_Return False
37232>>>>>        End
37232>>>>>>
37232>>>>>        
37232>>>>>        Send Request_Save of hoUserDD
37233>>>>>        Function_Return (not(Err))
