37639>>>    // Add code to customize your Zoom View based on how it was invoked.
37639>>>    // Use NavigateData to determine the context this view will be used in.
37639>>>    Procedure OnNavigateForward tWebNavigateData NavigateData Integer hoInvokingView Integer hoInvokingObject
37642>>>
37642>>>        // if this view is being used in multiple contexts, you may need a block of code
37642>>>        // like this to handle customizations. This would include hiding rows and buttons
37642>>>        // (WebSet pbRender) and changing the values of various captions.
37642>>>        Case Begin
37642>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromMain)
