38554>>>    Procedure SetActionButtons
38557>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38557>>>        tWebNavigateData NavigateData
38557>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
38557>>>        Handle hoDD
38557>>>
38557>>>        Get Server to hoDD
38558>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
38559>>>        
38559>>>        If (hoDD) Begin
38561>>>            Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
38562>>>        End
38562>>>>
38562>>>        Else Begin
38563>>>            Move False to bHasRecord
38564>>>        End
