38589>>>        Case Begin
38589>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromMain)
38591>>>                // If from main, this is a probably a main file Select to Zoom.
38591>>>                // This is the most typical way to navigate to a zoom.
38591>>>                Case Break
38592>>>                
38592>>>            Case (NavigateData.eNavigateType = nfFromParent)
38595>>>                // If from parent, this is a constrained drill down.
38595>>>                // If needed, you could check NavigateData.iTable to determine the constraining parent.
